work.title: Musik til Adam Oehlenschlägers skuespil "Aladdin eller Den forunderlige Lampe", opus 34
Music for Adam Oehlenschläger's Play 'Aladdin or the Wonderful Lamp', Opus 34
Dramatisk eventyr i fem akter
Dramatic Fairy Tale in Five Acts

history.p: In early 1917, The Royal Theatre laid plans for a new production of Oehlenschläger's 'dramatic fairy tale', Aladdin. Nielsen was eventually persuaded to compose the music, and after some preliminary drafts in 1917 he composed the music mainly over a seven-month period from July 1918 to January 1919.
